KPM Database Design
Database Philosophy
The database is centered around one object:
Project
Everything else either belongs directly to a project or indirectly through a feature or sprint.
The hierarchy becomes:
Organization
    │
    ├── Members
    │
    └── Projects
            │
            ├── Team Members
            ├── Modules
            │      └── Features
            │              ├── Deliverables
            │              ├── Reviews
            │              └── Comments
            │
            ├── Sprints
            ├── Meetings
            ├── Documents
            └── Activity Logs

